    "custom_liquid_xeYTyp": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap');\n  .faq-wrap{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 20px;}\n  .faq-eyebrow{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#CB572A;margin-bottom:10px;}\n  .faq-heading{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(28px,6vw,42px);font-weight:400;color:#1a1a1a;line-height:1.15;margin:0 0 36px;}\n  .faq-heading em{font-style:italic;color:#CB572A;}\n  .faq-item{border-top:1px solid #e8e2dc;overflow:hidden;}\n  .faq-item:last-child{border-bottom:1px solid #e8e2dc;}\n  .faq-q{width:100%;background:none;border:none;padding:20px 0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;cursor:pointer;text-align:left;gap:16px;}\n  .faq-q-text{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:#1a1a1a;line-height:1.4;}\n  .faq-icon{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid #CB572A;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;transition:background 0.25s,transform 0.3s;}\n  .faq-icon svg{width:12px;height:12px;transition:transform 0.3s;}\n  .faq-icon svg line{stroke:#CB572A;stroke-width:1.8;stroke-linecap:round;}\n  .faq-item.open .faq-icon{background:#CB572A;transform:rotate(45deg);}\n  .faq-item.open .faq-icon svg line{stroke:#fff;}\n  .faq-body{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height 0.35s ease,padding 0.3s;}\n  .faq-item.open .faq-body{max-height:200px;}\n  .faq-body-inner{padding:0 0 20px;font-size:14px;color:#666;line-height:1.75;}\n  .faq-body-inner strong{color:#CB572A;font-weight:500;}\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"faq-wrap\">\n  <div class=\"faq-eyebrow\">Got questions?</div>\n  <h2 class=\"faq-heading\">Everything you need<br>to know about your<br><em>new brow pen</em></h2>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item open\">\n    <button class=\"faq-q\" onclick=\"toggle(this)\">\n      <span class=\"faq-q-text\">Does it actually look like real brows, or does it look drawn on?</span>\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\"><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"6\" y2=\"11\"/><line x1=\"1\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"11\" y2=\"6\"/></svg></span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-body\">\n      <div class=\"faq-body-inner\">Yes — that's the whole point. The micro-fork tip draws <strong>individual hair-like strokes</strong> that blend seamlessly into your natural brows. No blocky lines, no painted-on look. Just clean, realistic definition that people will genuinely think you were born with.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"faq-q\" onclick=\"toggle(this)\">\n      <span class=\"faq-q-text\">Will it smudge or fade during the day?</span>\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\"><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"6\" y2=\"11\"/><line x1=\"1\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"11\" y2=\"6\"/></svg></span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-body\">\n      <div class=\"faq-body-inner\">Not a chance. The formula is <strong>waterproof and sweat-resistant</strong> — it sets quickly and holds all day, whether you're at the gym, in the heat, or out for a long night. No touch-ups needed.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"faq-q\" onclick=\"toggle(this)\">\n      <span class=\"faq-q-text\">I've never used a microblading pen before. Is it hard to apply?</span>\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\"><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"6\" y2=\"11\"/><line x1=\"1\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"11\" y2=\"6\"/></svg></span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-body\">\n      <div class=\"faq-body-inner\">Not at all. The pen is designed to be <strong>beginner-friendly</strong> — just use short, light strokes in the direction of your natural hairs. Start sparse and build up. Most people get it right on their first try. And if you make a mistake? Just wipe it off and start over.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-item\">\n    <button class=\"faq-q\" onclick=\"toggle(this)\">\n      <span class=\"faq-q-text\">How is this different from a regular eyebrow pencil?</span>\n      <span class=\"faq-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\"><line x1=\"6\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"6\" y2=\"11\"/><line x1=\"1\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"11\" y2=\"6\"/></svg></span>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq-body\">\n      <div class=\"faq-body-inner\">A regular pencil fills in your brows as a solid shape — which often looks heavy or unnatural. Our pen uses a <strong>precision fork tip</strong> to mimic actual hair strokes, giving you a textured, dimensional result that looks like microblading — without the needle, the cost, or the commitment.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  function toggle(btn){\n    const item=btn.closest('.faq-item');\n    const isOpen=item.classList.contains('open');\n    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i=>i.classList.remove('open'));\n    if(!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');\n  }\n</script>",
